title: Alec’s Ice Cream Variety 4-pack Order ships & arrives separately | 10 Servings
description: I scream, you scream, it’s time for better ice cream—and here’s your chance to have it! Alec’s is the first premium ice cream made with A2 dairy (which may be more easily digestible) produced using holistic and sustainable farming practices. This variety pack comes in four delightfully decadent flavors: Strawberry Crumble, Peanut Butter Fudge Honeycomb, Banana Chocolate Date, and Triple Chocolate Blackout Cookie. Just one spoonful, and it’s easy to see why Alec’s is better than the rest!

To ensure the highest quality when you receive your ice cream, the pints will come in a separate box from your meals. Your ice cream box may arrive a few days after your meal box. Ice cream should be stored frozen.

